Harvest Capital Credit Corp extends revolving period and reduces pricing on credit facility
Wednesday, 23 Sep 2015 07:37am EDT 
Harvest Capital Credit Corp:Has amended its senior secured revolving credit facility with CapitalSource and City National Bank to, among other things, extend the revolving period and reduce pricing under the Facility.Revolving period under the Facility was extended by 18 months to April 30, 2017.Stated interest rate on the Facility was reduced from the applicable LIBOR rate plus 4.50% to the applicable LIBOR rate plus 3.25%.Final maturity date of the Facility of Oct. 29, 2018 remains unchanged. 
			
