	Article VIII

	.




	 




	“

	Excess Availability

	” shall mean, the amount, as determined by Agent in its discretion, calculated at any date, equal to Availability,

	minus

	the amount of all then outstanding and unpaid Obligations of Borrower.




	 




	 




	 


