	Fair Value

	” shall mean (i) as it relates to any Underlying Loan that is a Level 3 Asset (as defined in FAS 157), the “fair value” assigned to such Underlying Loan pursuant to the most recent valuation report received by Agent pursuant to

	Section 6.1(j)

	hereof;

	provided



	,



