	(c)     contractually or structurally subordinates such Pledged Loan by operation of a priority of payments, turnover provisions, the transfer of assets in order to limit recourse to the related Underlying Borrower or the granting of Liens (other than customary permitted Liens) on any of the Underlying Collateral; or




	 




