	7.14     Change in Business





	 




	Harvest shall not engage in any business in a manner that would violate in any material respect the applicable Credit Policy, the Investment Company Act, or any Applicable Law applicable to Harvest as a BDC. Harvest will at all times comply with any portfolio diversification and similar requirements set forth in the Investment Company Act applicable to business development companies. Harvest will at all times, subject to applicable grace periods and similar cure periods set forth in the Code, comply with the portfolio diversification and similar requirements set forth in the Code applicable to RICs.




	 





